<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
Gompers statement -- A headline in Wednesday's edition said that San Diego 
Unified School District Board of Trustees President Kay Davis "and her 
colleagues" stood behind a statement labeling a recent statewide honor for 
Gompers Secondary School as a farce. The phrase and her colleagues should have 
been omitted. 
</P>
