-- LABOR RELATIONS; AEROSPACE INDUSTRY -- LAYOFFS; AEROSPACE INDUSTRY -- LOS 
ANGELES COUNTY; AEROSPACE INDUSTRY -- GEORGIA; LOCKHEED AERONAUTICAL SYSTEMS 
CO; ADVANCED TACTICAL FIGHTER (AIRPLANE) 
</P>
