TREATIES -- USSR; CHEMICAL WARFARE; CHEMICAL WEAPONS -- USSR; CHEMICAL WEAPONS 
-- UNITED STATES; NUCLEAR WEAPONS -- USSR; NUCLEAR WEAPONS -- UNITED STATES 
</P>
