<P>
FBI BREAKS COLOMBIAN COCAINE RING IN NEW YORK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NEW YORK 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Federal authorities said Tuesday that they have broken up a large Colombian 
smuggling ring that had been selling $20-million to $25-million worth of 
cocaine in the New York area each month. 
</P>
</TEXT>
