<TEXT>
<P>
Officials from the Sun Carnival Assn. hope to move the John Hancock Bowl to New 
Year's Day. 
</P>
<P>
"The game's tentatively set to go Dec. 29," Hancock Bowl official Marc Boehm 
said. "But there's an NFL game at 1 p.m. on NBC between the Chicago Bears and 
the Kansas City Chiefs. And it's very difficult to go against the NFL." 
</P>
</TEXT>
