NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
George Allen, in his first year as football coach at Cal State Long Beach, has 
canceled the team's spring game, scheduled for Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
"It's the logical thing to do. . . . We're too short in personnel," Allen said. 
"Not because of injuries, though. We just don't have enough players yet." 
</P>
