matriculate to UCLA as a 400-meter intermediate hurdler. ; Photo, With help 
from Coach Tom McMurray, above, Beck refined his technique. ; Photo, Beck 
shattered a 15-year meet record in the conference championships. KIRBY LEE / 
for The Times 
</P>
