<P>
Photo, La Quinta Golf Course near Palm Springs is one of several owned by 
Landmark Land and part of deal with Barry G. Hon. Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
S&amp;L regulations have stalled Barry G. Hon's bid to buy resort properties. 
KARI RENE HALL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
