<DATE>
<P>
May 9, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
PASCUALE VALITUTTI 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 3; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
